| A04 – Insecure Design | No rate limiting; no payload limits; inline data | 🟠 High |
| A05 – Security Misconfiguration | No security headers; no CORS policy; no error handler | 🟠 High |
| A07 – Identification & Auth Failures | No authentication anywhere | 🔴 Critical |
| A09 – Security Logging Failures | No logging | 🔵 Low |

